&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;We are seeking a detail-oriented and analytical&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Business Analyst&lt;/strong&gt; with expertise in &lt;strong&gt;data analysis, PSA tools and Salesforce (SFDC)&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;The ideal candidate will bridge business needs and technical solutions, leveraging data-driven insights to optimize processes and support strategic decision-making.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain dashboards for security metrics, vulnerability trends, and operational KPIs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use SQL and scripting (Python preferred) for data extraction, transformation, and analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Configure and customize secure workflows, access controls, and compliance reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze PSA &amp;amp; CRM data to identify patterns impacting profitability and operational efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide day-to-day operational support for services, business systems and processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot and resolve issues related to data integrity, reporting, and system functionality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure adherence to operational workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Process Improvement: Identify gaps in security and operational processes, propose solutions, and assist in implementation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Testing &amp;amp; Validation: Support UAT and ensure deliverables meet both business and security requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain clear documentation for requirements, processes, and compliance standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
