&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with &lt;strong&gt;professional services automation management platforms (Certinia, Teamwork).&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hands-on experience with Salesforce (SFDC) configuration and reporting.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
