&lt;li&gt;Experience implementing cross-functional cost governance processes and KPIs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years as a Business Analyst or similar role in &lt;strong&gt;software or cybersecurity &lt;/strong&gt;environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent verbal and written communication skills for stakeholder engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong problem-solving and critical thinking abilities.&lt;/li&gt;
