&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: .375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 7pt; color: black;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 11.0pt;&quot;&gt;The Lead&amp;nbsp;Product Owner&amp;nbsp;role will&amp;nbsp;lead&amp;nbsp;the strategy, design, and continuous improvement of enterprise business systems and processes. This role owns the end-to-end product vision for assigned platform capabilities—directly enabling operational efficiency, data integrity, and cross-functional alignment across the organization.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: .375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 7pt; color: black;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 11.0pt;&quot;&gt;As a Product Owner, you will work at the intersection of business stakeholders, operations, and IT, translating strategic goals into scalable, data-driven solutions. You will define the roadmap, drive cross-functional execution, and champion automation and system visibility across key business processes. Core platform ownership includes Salesforce CRM and its integrations across the enterprise technology stack.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: .375in; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 7pt; color: black;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 11.0pt;&quot;&gt;This is a high-impact, cross-functional role&amp;nbsp;that requires&amp;nbsp;strategic thinking&amp;nbsp;and strong execution. The role&amp;nbsp;thrives in solving complex business challenges through systems, data, and process optimization.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: .375in; margin-top: 1pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold; font-family: Arial; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #5a2a82;&quot;&gt;Essential Functions/Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;  margin-top: 0in; m

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Black Duck Software, Inc. helps organizations build secure, high-quality software, minimizing risks while maximizing speed and productivity. Black Duck, a recognized pioneer in application security, provides SAST, SCA, and DAST solutions that enable teams to quickly find and fix vulnerabilities and defects in proprietary code, open source components, and application behavior. With a combination of industry-leading tools, services, and expertise, only Black Duck helps organizations maximize security and quality in DevSecOps and throughout the software development life cycle.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;This individual contributor must be highly motivated and a proven sales executive in the Federal Civilian market with demonstrated experience selling to software development and security teams. The Lead Regional Sales Manager will report to the Vice President of Public Sector, and will work closely with his or her Sales Engineer, Public Sector Marketing Manager, Sales Development Representative, and Renewal Representative.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;A principal goal for this position is the selling of enterprise agreements within the Federal Civilian territory to achieve the bookings target. The position requires extensive relationship building activities, discovery of prospect requirements, developing a solution that meets the requirements, and developing a quantifiable business case that ensure the customer is obtaining the maximum value. To achieve this along with further adoption, the Regional Sales Manager must have strong skills and experience in selling complex solutions in large and complicated customer environments.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ewa-rteLine&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
